2025-11-28 14:06:06|guardian_store|359|USE `guardian_store`;
EXPLAIN
SELECT 
                    d.id as dashboard_id,
                    d.dashboard_uid,
                    d.dashboard_name,
                    o.org_name,
                    f.folder_name,
                    COUNT(e.id) as execution_count,
                    COUNT(DISTINCT e.user_id) as unique_users,
                    COUNT(DISTINCT e.template_id) as unique_queries,
                    SUM(CASE WHEN t.is_heavy THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as heavy_query_count
                FROM grafana_dashboards d
                LEFT JOIN grafana_folders f ON d.folder_id = f.id
                LEFT JOIN grafana_organizations o ON d.org_id = o.org_id
                LEFT JOIN grafana_query_executions e ON d.id = e.dashboard_id
                LEFT JOIN grafana_query_templates t ON e.template_id = t.id
                WHERE e.date = '2025-11-27'
                GROUP BY d.id, d.dashboard_uid, d.dashboard_name, o.org_name, f.folder_name
                ORDER BY execution_count DESC
                LIMIT 10;

2025-12-02 12:47:04|guardian_store|266|USE `guardian_store`;
EXPLAIN
SELECT e.executed_at, t.hash, t.normalized_query, t.sample_raw_query as raw_query, 
                              t.weight, t.is_heavy, t.has_now_pattern, t.now_window, 
                              t.time_window, t.has_short_window
                       FROM influxdb_query_executions e
                       JOIN influxdb_query_templates t ON e.template_id = t.id

QueryHistory.30:
2025-12-02 12:55:09|guardian_store|250|USE `guardian_store`;
EXPLAIN
SELECT t.normalized_query, 
                          COUNT(e.id) as count,
                          t.weight as avg_weight,
                          t.time_window,
                          t.now_window,
                          t.sample_raw_query as raw_query,
                          COALESCE(MAX(d.dashboard_name), MAX(qoc.dashboard_name)) as dashboard_name,
                          COALESCE(MAX(p.panel_title), MAX(qoc.panel_title)) as panel_title,
                          COALESCE(MAX(o.org_name), MAX(qoc.org_name)) as org_name
                   FROM influxdb_query_templates t
                   JOIN influxdb_query_executions e ON t.id = e.template_id
                   LEFT JOIN query_origin_cache qoc ON t.hash = qoc.influxdb_query_hash
                   LEFT JOIN grafana_template_mappings tm ON qoc.grafana_template_id = tm.template_id
                   LEFT JOIN grafana_dashboards d ON tm.dashboard_uid = d.dashboard_uid
                   LEFT JOIN grafana_panels p ON tm.panel_id = p.panel_uid AND tm.dashboard_uid = p.dashboard_uid
                   LEFT JOIN grafana_organizations o ON d.org_id = o.org_id
                   WHERE e.executed_at >= '2025-12-01 00:00:00' AND e.executed_at <= '2025-12-02 00:00:00' AND t.is_heavy = TRUE
                   GROUP BY t.id, t.normalized_query, t.weight, t.time_window, t.now_window, t.sample_raw_query
                   ORDER BY count DESC
                   LIMIT 100;

                   FROM influxdb_query_templates t

                   LEFT JOIN query_origin_cache qoc ON t.hash = qoc.influxdb_query_hash
                   LEFT JOIN grafana_template_mappings tm ON qoc.grafana_template_id = tm.template_id

                   GROUP BY t.id, t.normalized_query, t.weight, t.time_window, t.now_window, t.sample_raw_query
